        <p>
            TechVendo is all about changing how tech fans trade by enabling direct peer-to-peer transactions with transparency and reliability.

            Our goal is to connect buyers and sellers in a trustworthy environment where everyone feels confident. Whether you're upgrading your gaming setup, improving your workstation, or clearing out old tech, TechVendo is the place to be.

